com.nandox.jop.core.processor.expression

Interface PageExpression

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PageWriteExpression
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPageExpression, BooleanPageExpression, CollectionPageExpression, SimplePageExpression

    public interface PageExpression
    Represent generic page expression.

    An expression is java (or other) language expression used in page into html attribute or jbean tag

    Author:
    Fernando Costantino
